CSV Fixer is a simple app created in WinForms C# and it was mainly designed to handle one line .CSV files. If you know the number of columns you can enter it manually, or you can choose from the drop-down list which is automatically generated.
In the future I plan to expand it’s functionality or better use part of it’s code for other projects.
